Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.54,0:18:44.66,OPLetreros,Caption,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,445)\fscx170\fscy170\bord2.0}ECENA 2 - EQUIPE QUE ENTRE{\alpha&HFF&}GARÁ CAESAR
