Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.08,0:21:19.52,Main,Zoro,0,0,0,,Te peguei!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.52,0:21:23.34,Main,Zoro,0,0,0,,Vou pegar minha espada.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.84,0:21:34.91,Main,Wicca,0,0,0,,Droga!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.91,0:21:40.22,Main,Wicca,0,0,0,,Que problema!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.22,0:21:41.60,Main,Wicca,0,0,0,,Sou muito desastrada!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.60,0:21:43.52,Main,Wicca,0,0,0,,O humano vai me ver!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.23,0:21:46.70,Main,Wicca,0,0,0,,Preciso fugir antes que o humano...
