Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.28,0:23:44.29,Main,Momonosuke,0,0,0,,{\an8}Não!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.29,0:23:46.87,Main,Momonosuke,0,0,0,,{\an8}Você não deve beber tudo!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.87,0:23:48.00,Main,Momonosuke,0,0,0,,Escute!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.00,0:23:52.44,Main,Momonosuke,0,0,0,,Um degustador de veneno deve\N beber um pouco para se certificar...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.44,0:23:56.48,Main,Momonosuke,0,0,0,,...de que a comida que o shogun\N vai comer não está envenenada.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.48,0:23:57.50,Main,Momonosuke,0,0,0,,Entendeu?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.50,0:23:58.82,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,Sim.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.82,0:24:00.60,Main,Momonosuke,0,0,0,,Faça de novo!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.60,0:24:02.75,Main,Momonosuke,0,0,0,,Traga o chá, Chopperemon!
