Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.88,0:24:12.34,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,Meu senhor, como está se sentindo?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.34,0:24:14.60,Main,Momonosuke,0,0,0,,Estou muito satisfeito.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.26,0:24:18.40,Main,Momonosuke,0,0,0,,Estou muito contente.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.40,0:24:19.87,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,Sério?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.87,0:24:22.24,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,Fico feliz que esteja assim.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.26,0:24:26.02,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,Eu também estou muito satisfeito!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.86,0:24:35.30,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,I-Isso doeu, Nami-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.26,0:24:38.90,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,Isso não é uma festa \Nde dormir no colo?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.90,0:24:40.46,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,Não existem festas assim!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.46,0:24:43.70,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,Estamos brincando de shogun.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.70,0:24:45.76,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,Brincando de shogun?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.76,0:24:52.30,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,Momo fica deprimido sempre que está sozinho, parece que algo sério o preocupa.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.30,0:24:54.38,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,Ele não nos conta.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.38,0:24:58.24,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,Ele pode ser uma criança, mas parece \Nque tem cicatrizes no coração.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.24,0:24:59.28,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,Sério?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.28,0:25:03.01,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,Então é isso...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.01,0:25:04.94,Main,Momonosuke,0,0,0,,Ei, senhor ossos!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.94,0:25:05.32,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,Sim?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.70,0:25:08.25,Main,Momonosuke,0,0,0,,Me divirta e faça bem feito!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.25,0:25:12.52,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,Não, eu só sigo as \Nordens de Luffy-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.52,0:25:13.47,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,Faça isso!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.52,0:25:19.83,Main,Brook song,0,0,0,,Não!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.83,0:25:24.03,Main,Brook song,0,0,0,,Não, não!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.03,0:25:28.31,Main,Brook song,0,0,0,,Talvez você tenha me enterrado, talvez você tenha me enterrado,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.31,0:25:32.44,Main,Brook song,0,0,0,,mas eu sempre voltarei.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.44,0:25:33.58,Main,Everyone,0,0,0,,Sim!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.44,0:25:33.58,Secondary,Everyone,0,0,0,,Sim!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.58,0:25:39.55,Main,Brook song,0,0,0,,Corpo cheio de vitalidade!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.55,0:25:40.50,Main,Brook song,0,0,0,,Vamos!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.02,0:25:48.24,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,Obrigado a todos.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.70,0:25:56.70,Main,Jora,0,0,0,,Eu não gosto!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.70,0:26:01.94,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,Mas não deveria haver mais ninguém no navio.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.94,0:26:03.85,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,Isso mesmo.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.85,0:26:05.76,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,O que foi esse som?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.76,0:26:06.71,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,Que medo!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.71,0:26:08.18,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,Que medo!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.18,0:26:09.45,Main,Momonosuke,0,0,0,,Onami!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.45,0:26:13.12,Main,Jora,0,0,0,,Eu odeio isso, droga!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.12,0:26:17.32,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,V-Vem do quarto dos homens.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.32,0:26:19.36,Main,Jora,0,0,0,,Oh, que ruim!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.46,0:26:23.96,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,Realmente tem alguém aí!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.96,0:26:25.30,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,De quem é essa voz?!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.32,0:26:28.43,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,510)\fad(250,0)\bord2.0\fscx180\fscy180}COLISEU CORRIDA
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.86,0:26:31.97,Main,Staff,0,0,0,,Participante Capman, do Bloco B...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.97,0:26:34.20,Main,Staff,0,0,0,,Está aí?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.20,0:26:36.19,Main,Staff,0,0,0,,Participante Bartolomeo?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.62,0:26:44.82,Main,Staff,0,0,0,,Oh, você é Bartolomeo, certo?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.42,0:26:47.58,Main,Staff,0,0,0,,O Bloco B está prestes a começar.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.98,0:26:53.24,Main,Staff,0,0,0,,A propósito, você sabe onde está o participante Capman?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.64,0:26:57.60,Main,Bartolomeo,0,0,0,,Não faço ideia.
